WEBVTT

00:00:01.320 --> 00:00:02.800
Strah me je.

00:00:03.328 --> 00:00:04.335
Trenutno,

00:00:05.096 --> 00:00:06.617
na ovoj bini,

00:00:06.641 --> 00:00:07.859
ja osjećam strah.

00:00:09.089 --> 00:00:10.818
Nisam upoznao mnogo ljudi u životu,

00:00:10.818 --> 00:00:13.046
koji bi jasno priznali kada se plaše.

00:00:13.580 --> 00:00:15.865
To je zato jer duboko u njima

00:00:15.865 --> 00:00:17.240
znaju kako se lako širi.

00:00:18.345 --> 00:00:20.078
Vidiš, strah je kao bolest.

00:00:20.907 --> 00:00:23.412
Kada se širi, širi se kao požar.

00:00:23.918 --> 00:00:25.196
Ali, šta se desi kada,

00:00:25.206 --> 00:00:26.494
u lice tog straha

00:00:27.297 --> 00:00:28.687
uradiš ono što moraš?

00:00:29.297 --> 00:00:30.604
To se zove hrabrost.